window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>She wants my help and I want her in my bed.</b></p> <p>I'm used to women chasing me, but she's the first one to knock on my front door. Like the gentleman I pretend to be, I let her in—with plans to seduce her, to get her to yield to me.</p> <p>Then she tells me her life is in danger and asks for my protection in the form of marriage. It'll be nothing more than a front, a guise to mask our intentions. Yet the lust burning in me is real. So is this unusual possessiveness.</p> <p>And my bride-to-be? She's either a good actress... Or she desires me with a fierceness I've never seen.</p> <p>To get that from her? To have a part of her no one else has? I'd kill for it. And I may have to because of the threats surrounding us.</p> <p><i>This is book two in the Dark &amp; Dirty Vows series which is intended for mature listeners. Welcome to the dark side...</i></p>"; 
